{"tid":752160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[中國武術]大陸果個徐曉冬真係型到仆街","createTime":"2018-07-22T14:33:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T12:46:25.000Z","uid":60455,"like":76,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"7a3f0f5b8fb3901ae74502a75e09358772e32809","tid":752160,"uid":60455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T14:33:20.000Z","msg":"可能Old news左，但真係好欣賞佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚夠薑踼爆成個傳統武術界個問題，再講埋中國人個民族主義意識<br />\n<br />\n徐曉冬專訪完整版：一百年內沒有人像我這樣揭開中國武術的黑幕<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=a8TMTLU3Fck\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Da8TMTLU3Fck&d=P%2BOEcJrfLO2NIue6jitwWr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=d84b3dd7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=a8TMTLU3Fck</a>"},{"pid":"eda953cfdb5d1b39fb4226a5cf96e49ef363f2a0","tid":752160,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T14:36:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2b34f997905c005d07f148bc10c3d90d527b1b5c","tid":752160,"uid":16061,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T14:46:01.000Z","msg":"可唔可以叫佢打鳩氣功個啲戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾十個人比一條友彈到老西咁遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d7a5e27c3f31d7c030aedb26ab289781c1a761a","tid":752160,"uid":53705,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T14:58:19.000Z","msg":"其實佢可以生存咁耐都算奇蹟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為佢踢爆左好多 所謂既「武林高手」係呃人, 斷人米路<br />\n照計D「武林高手」應該會請 刀手去殺佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就好似之前有個 記者 踢爆地溝油<br />\n結果個記者就比人當街斬死左.........<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eb014944bedc0171086f4d46f77046ec51676db","tid":752160,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T14:59: